data.description: This great home in a quiet neighborhood won't last long! Entry connects to both formal and casual living areas. Versatile floor plan allows you to utilize each area to fit your needs. Front room could be formal living/dining/office/etc. Newer updates include interior paint, new interior doors, molding, carpet, vinyl planking & custom barn doors for pantry, and black stainless appliances. Built-in cabinets in open kitchen dining area provide lots of storage. Four bedrooms and 2 baths upstairs. Master bedroom features ensuite & 2 large closets. Don't miss unique light fixture/fan in master bath w/Bluetooth music capabilities & water-proof remote. Fenced back yard with patio, raised garden beds, and storage shed. Come make this your new home!
